Level 60 Druid of Xegony<BR>
Havenlight</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubroomhilda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Broomhilda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1660<br> <font color=#333399>(6/5/02 3:04:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27516.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> LOL, its kinda funny how everythign takes whining to get changed, or put in right.  From Uber guild loots to quest items, Verant seems to rely on the whining to gauge what needs adjusting.  Especially now with their new philosophy of underpowering the rewards until people whine about how weak the reward is.  <br>
